# COMPONENT

## BlogComponent

### PACKAGE

org.simplemodeling.textus.blog

### DESCRIPTION

Blog CAR component used as a Cozy development driver.

This model keeps the image binding pattern explicit:
- CNCF Blob metadata stores image metadata.
- CNCF BlobAttachment Association links BlogPost to one or more image Blobs by
  role.
- `BlogPost.authorAccountId` ties blog authoring to a user account.
- `BlogPost` supports draft, published, and inactive states.
- Public blog read/search exposes published active posts.
- `BlogPost.content` stores the canonical HTML article fragment.
- `ImportPostTree` accepts a local-previewable HTML file tree archive and uses
  CNCF standard HTML tree values to extract article content.
- `BlogInlineImage` tracks images discovered from `img` tags in article content.

# SERVICE

