# VALUE

## BlogEntityImageSpec

### DESCRIPTION

Image specification for Entity-level BlogPost image bindings such as thumbnail,
primary, cover, and gallery.

### ATTRIBUTE

| name            | type     | multiplicity |
|-----------------+----------+--------------|
| path            | string   | ?            |
| existingBlobId  | entityid | ?            |
| role            | string   | 1            |
| sortOrder       | int      | ?            |
| caption         | string   | ?            |
| contentType     | string   | ?            |
| checksum        | string   | ?            |

## BlogInlineImageSpec

### DESCRIPTION

Image specification for an image embedded in Blog HTML content. File-tree import
uses `path` resolved relative to the entry HTML. Direct bulk registration may
use `clientId` for `cid:` references.

### ATTRIBUTE

| name            | type     | multiplicity |
|-----------------+----------+--------------|
| clientId        | string   | ?            |
| path            | string   | ?            |
| existingBlobId  | entityid | ?            |
| contentType     | string   | ?            |
| altText         | string   | ?            |
| titleText       | string   | ?            |
| sortOrder       | int      | ?            |
| checksum        | string   | ?            |

